Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二级的台阶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能在晚上就变成了十三级了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我害怕魔之十三台阶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还怎么扩展地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来加入我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要加入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲在哪里 给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上存在着 无法看见的黑暗住人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们偶尔也会显露獠牙 袭击你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他 正是为从它们手中保护你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从地狱深渊前来的 正义使者…也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校的七不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔之十三台阶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.03,1:59:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拦住他 别让他得逞
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.03,1:59:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小广
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想的美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁快点拦住小广
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 小广好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爱玩这种无聊的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙天地 興我力量 降伏群魔 迎来曙光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾人左手 所封百鬼 尊我号令 只在此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天地混沌 乾坤蒼范 人世蒙塵 鬼怪猖狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空海闊 鬼面仏心 鬼哭啾啾 霊感散消
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怨恨的念波相當强烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还得花很长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时还是别让孩子们接近的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鵺野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,律子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 鼻血...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 这好像是刚刚从椅子跌下来撞到才流出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本杂志绝对不是色情的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看色情的书还比较健全一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是很健全的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那个...律子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是找我有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师你班上的学生小广他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说要去调查旧校舍那个十三级台阶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我阻止过了 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是...魔之十三台阶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在白天只有十二级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上数的话会变成十三级了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏到第十三级台阶的人会消失 永远也回不来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村 你够了没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你吓死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 还是来看看这台阶是不是真的有十三级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么 不要推我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乡子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是白天 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是十二级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是十二级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么魔之十三台阶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真能扯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正学校的怪谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的笑话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔之十三台阶的故事是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些只是谣传而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算是真的你们也看不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 把小手放在膝盖上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴拉上拉链
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔之十三台阶只有坏孩子才看得到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你们这样的乖小孩呢 是看不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 我们又不是幼稚园小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 片名干脆改一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后就叫地狱保父阿鵺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 第五堂课开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 阿鵺那家伙怎么会带上除灵工具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真仓翔的妖怪大百科时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 真怨恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本 四这个数字会让人联想到死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不吉利 所以被大家讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个大家应该都知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以日本的医院还有酒店一般都没有四号房
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 真怨恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的在国外 人们都不喜欢十三这个数字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以美国的医院跟酒店一般都没有十三号房哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 真怨恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会不喜欢十三呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为背叛耶稣的犹大是他第十三个弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 真怨恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且背叛那天又正好是十三号星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 真怨恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:09:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人说死刑台的台阶有十三级
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有各种的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是真正的理由还没定案呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 请节哀顺便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们请一个同学来解这个题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.03,1:59:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚刚还在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿这小子没办法啊 又跷课了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第十三级台阶只有坏孩子才看得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可能可以看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是挺坏的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像现在这样子经常跷课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅长在墙上胡乱涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘车经常不买票
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从老爸钱包里偷钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买零食吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺的班上都是好学生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他们真难相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得和他们只是泛泛之交
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止还没有人要好的叫我克也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像只有我格格不入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 是阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我乖乖的回到座位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后天就要举行全国性的模拟考了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天 明天都有课后补习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后大家都要留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大家都给我用功一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是年级第一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a7}(目标是年级第一)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可以输给其他班哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起无谓的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把试题给偷出来不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有高桥老师一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高桥老师 阿鵺请你到五年三班教室去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鵺野老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你又在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 原来你也是来偷试卷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真是志同道合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是三班的 木村克也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一班的佐佐木 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们真是坏学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得是哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克也 你很有前途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我克也吗 好高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次有学校的同学这样叫我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要加入我们的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都集合在旧校舍的屋顶上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么多伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好伙伴 等着你来加入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没叫我来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,律子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很了解你找理由想要见我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢 我现在正在帮学生补习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是木村君他...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 木村又像平常一样跷课了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个臭小子...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的补习到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 谁来帮我找一下木村在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他在一起真的好轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟我一样都是扯后腿的不良学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这样才称得上真正的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是魔之十三台阶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 要从这里上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面大家都在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想见他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会告诉你这个十三台阶的故事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多在十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个学校里个超级不良学生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的时候会拿刀子威胁老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是到超市去偷便当 为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有一天 他潜入学校想放火的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被值班老师发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就想从这个台阶逃到屋顶上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是脚滑了一下就滚了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摔断了脖子 当场死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自此以后这台阶只要坏学生踩上后就会变成十三级
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而踏进第十三级的学生会被吸进那家伙的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也出不来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他想要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想 不良学生不是都喜欢成群结队的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 他一直在找合得来的不良学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是..是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们两个不就很危险了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 你不要推我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得有点心神不宁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快点找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊 快上去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 居然有十三级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 为什么停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因 因为有第十三级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又 又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可能会被拉进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个死掉的不良学生就叫佐佐木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从上面传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是不良学生的天堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不良学生要和不良学生好好相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来 救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前已经好几次想要超度这里的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他们根本对我的话充耳不闻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不应该因为是小孩子就纵容他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺 他们是小孩幽灵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我克也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克也 我一定会救你出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为是谁 原来是那个每天在外面念经的老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙要成为我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开克也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要成为这种家伙的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们想要被超度 我可以帮助你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话 我就用鬼手把你们全部消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做就试试看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们早就知道你不会对小孩子出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小广
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙要搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟前面说的不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是没有朋友的坏学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么有这么多人来救他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别罗嗦了 把他拉进来就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干吗 不要指挥我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌别人命令我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克也不会交给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要装出一副好孩子的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心理扭曲也适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 臭小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来还想救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你们改过之前就待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙天地 興我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降伏群魔 迎来曙光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 这是这次考试的试卷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然是不良学生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没资格待在老师您的班上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你跟他们几个不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好好反省之心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是还有很多伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子咕噜咕噜的叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别磨磨蹭蹭 直接回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鵺也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来教学实习的玉藻老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我喜欢的类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对那种细细长长的没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟阿鵺之间简直就是月亮和鳖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs18}(月亮和鳖虽然都是圆的 但是完全相反 形容差距非常大)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像鲸鱼和灰尘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.05,0:22:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样讲太过分了吧
